* Mixed SCD\nStrategies
** Within Same Table
***_ Different columns → different SCD types
***_ e.g., email = Type 1, city = Type 2
** Hybrid Approach
***_ Type 1 for non-analytical attributes
***_ Type 2 for business-critical attributes
** Design Principle
***_ Don't apply Type 2 to everything
***_ Overhead only justified for key attributes
** Documentation
***_ Clearly document per-column SCD type
***_ Guide downstream consumers
@endmindmap
